Introduction

May (Korean: 메이; Japanese: メイ) is a Japanese singer and dancer formerly under FNC Entertainment and FNC W. She was a member and the Lead Dancer and Maknae of the South Korean girl group Cherry Bullet.

On January 21, 2019, she made her official debut as a member of the South Korean girl group Cherry Bullet with the single mini album "Let's Play Cherry Bullet" with "Q & A" serving as the title track.

In 2021, she participated in the Mnet survival show "Girls Planet 999". Unfortunately, on the 11th episode, which was aired on October 15, May was revealed to have been eliminated following the third round of eliminations.
